lines.text: That was pretty good. But you know, I'm still hungry.

[to Starvation personified]
Pardon me, buddy. That's probably the grocery man.
One month later... there comes to this snow-bound village, a poor, hungry little kitty cat.
Meow! Meow!... I'm that hungry little kitty cat you just read about... Meow! Meow!
The next day and 130° below zero... Seems authentic.
The weatherman's right. We'd better go South right away.
